active_skill.name: Magnetic Lock-On
active_skill.description:
Pulls in nearby enemies and deals Physical DMG to all enemies hit.

DMG Multiplier: 720%/768%/816%/864%/912%

Daze Multiplier: 421.5%/449.6%/477.7%/505.8%/533.9%

Cooldown 24s

additional_ability.name: Magnetic Attraction
additional_ability.description: When there is at least 1 Anomaly character in your squad: Active Skill attack range is increased, and DMG is increased by 30%/37.5%/45%/52.5%/60%.
